{"data":[{"date":"15:09 01/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Politano n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Inter?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/1/politano-phat-bieu-ve-inter-clb-moi-gia-nhap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Matteo Politano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Inter Milan, CLB m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp. Anh hy v\u1ecdng s\u00e2n Giuseppe Meazza ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mang l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Politano gia nh\u1eadp Inter</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Matteo Politano \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a Inter Milan trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng Radja Nainggolan, Stefan de Vrij v\u00e0 Roberto Gagliardini. Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, Inter d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed9c c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Lazio \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a Serie A m\u00f9a 2017/18, Inter \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Champions League. C\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Trung Qu\u1ed1c quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 Nerazurri c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Politano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Inter Milan, CLB m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Politano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Inter Milan, CLB m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/politano-phat-bieu-ve-inter-clb-moi-gia-nhap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Politano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Inter sau khi gia nh\u1eadp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPolitano ch\u01a1i cho Sassuolo m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Inter theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m sau.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nH\u00e1o h\u1ee9c ra s\u00e2n cho CLB m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft, Politano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Inter v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngay. \u201c<em>T\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t khi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i</em>\u201d, m\u0169i c\u00f4ng 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Inter TV. \u201c<em>T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch, CLB, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t</em>.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>T\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Sassuolo \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gia nh\u1eadp Inter. Giuseppe Meazza l\u00e0 s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i cho t\u00f4i may m\u1eafn. T\u00f4i t\u1eebng ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea3 Inter v\u00e0 Milan t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ghi b\u00e0n cho trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Inter</em>.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Politano \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0110T Italia d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV Roberto Mancini. Anh c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Inter tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mu-chot-57-trieu-bang-cho-hau-ve-cua-inter-milan-421-188723.html\">MU ch\u1ed1t 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Inter Milan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/icardi-muon-o-lai-inter-milan-trong-tuong-lai-176-187519.html\">S\u1ebfp Inter b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea v\u00e0 Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/2-doi-bong-italia-muon-danh-bai-mu-vu-sao-tottenham-172-187269.html\">2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i MU v\u1ee5 sao Tottenham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-giai-cuu-bom-xit-cua-chelsea-172-186963.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u bom x\u1ecbt c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3918","checkdouble":"190095"},{"date":"13:55 01/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 19h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/1/quang-ninh-vs-ha-noi-vong-17-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 17 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 1/7.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC v\u00f2ng 17 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 1/7.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/quang-ninh-vs-ha-noi-vong-17-vleague-2018-372-190090.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP QU\u1ea2NG NINH VS H\u00c0 N\u1ed8I</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3917","checkdouble":"190090"},{"date":"13:52 01/07","title":"Petr Cech khi\u1ebfn t\u00e2n binh 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo s\u1ee3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/petr-cech-khien-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang-cua-arsenal-cam-thay-lo-so.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno, c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Arsenal.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Bernd Leno</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/clb-arsenal-chinh-thuc-trinh-lang-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018-172-188980.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Bernd Leno </span>t\u1eeb Bayer Leverkusen. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u, nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i h\u1ecd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Petr-Cech-phat-bieu-ve-Bernd-Leno-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Bernd Leno</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n anh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Leno nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea9y Petr Cech ho\u1eb7c David Ospina ra \u0111i. Hi\u1ec7n Cech c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Ospina v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Petr Cech th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Leno</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno, c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cech thach thuc Leno cho vi tri so 1 trong khung go Arsenal\" title=\"Cech th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Leno cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/petr-cech-khien-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang-cua-arsenal-cam-thay-lo-so.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cech th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Leno cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Napoli nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Leno\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Leno l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho Arsenal, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Cech t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi m\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ospina s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates. Hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 v\u00e0 Italia mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3916","checkdouble":"190087"},{"date":"14:42 01/07","title":"Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Arsenal c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/chot-thoi-diem-arsenal-cong-bo-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira t\u1eeb Sampdoria, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Lucas Torreira</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRamsey ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Jack Wilshere ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. HLV Unai Emery bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/chot-thoi-diem-arsenal-cong-bo-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Lucas Torreira\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLucas Torreira c\u1ee7a Sampdoria l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsenal nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia. Ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n khi t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Torreira \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1edbi 36 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Sampdoria x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1eafp b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Uruguay \u1edf World Cup 2018, anh c\u0169ng tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. R\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Lucas Torreira khi\u1ebfn\u00a0Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-469-190073.html\" target=\"_blank\">Gary Neville khen Lucas Torreira</span>, c\u1ef1u sao M.U \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996, Gary Neville tin r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay t\u1edbi Emirates, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Arsenal s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 Torreira v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira t\u1eeb Sampdoria, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal chieu mo Torreira voi gia 30 trieu euro\" title=\"Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/chu-tich-sampdoria-xac-nhan-ban-sao-khung-cho-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 Lucas Torreira v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUruguay s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 6 th\u00e1ng 7, Torreira l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3915","checkdouble":"190091"},{"date":"14:58 01/07","title":"Liverpool \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Karius","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/28/liverpool-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-karius.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Loris Karius g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Loris Karius</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLoris Karius l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c mang v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Simon Mignolet.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Loris Karius \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Loris Karius \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/Tuong-lai-Loris-Karius-duoc-HLV-Klopp-quyet-dinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klopp ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Karius</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh Karius \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Mignolet \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong khung g\u1ed7. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1\u00a02018 v\u1edbi Real Madrid, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf 2/3 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Liverpool, khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-3. Sau nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda n\u00e0y Karius g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool n\u00ean t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Liverpool s\u1ebd mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed The Kop c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, theo The Sun v\u00e0 ESPN, HLV Klopp s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong khung g\u1ed7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, theo \u0111\u00f3 Karius ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a The Kop \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo ESPN, HLV Klopp s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf v\u00e0i ch\u1ee5c tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao nh\u01b0 Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma hay Courtois c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/liverpool-chap-nhan-that-bai-vu-thu-mon-79-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool kh\u00f4ng mua Alisson \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-liverpool-o-he-2018-172-181789.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Jack Butland</span> c\u1ee7a Stoke City, song th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Liverpool kh\u00f4ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Mignolet s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Anfield. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3914","checkdouble":"190092"},{"date":"15:30 01/07","title":"Napoli quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/7/20/hlv-conte-khang-dinh-ngung-theo-duoi-koulibaly.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kalidou Koulibaly ho\u1eb7c Dries Mertens c\u1ee7a Napoli, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao cho The Blues.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Napoli nh\u1ea3 Sarri cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u1ed9t ng\u1ed9t r\u1eddi Napoli d\u00f9 v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Carlo Ancelotti, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec9nh cao.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Napoli h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Napoli h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/Chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-2018-gap-kho-vu-sao-khung-Napoli-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Maurizio Sarri s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay Conte</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n gi\u1eefa Sarri v\u00e0 Napoli, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n San Paolo.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a HLV Sarri v\u1ec1 thay Conte, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ef1u HLV Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap The Blues c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, ngo\u00e0i ra \u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Chelsea s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i Conte v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri trong \u00edt gi\u1edd t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Napoli s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 sao kh\u1ee7ng cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kalidou Koulibaly ho\u1eb7c Dries Mertens c\u1ee7a Napoli, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao cho The Blues.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"koulibaly\" title=\"koulibaly\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/9/20/muc-tieu-cua-chelsea-gia-han-voi-napoli-them-5-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Napoli s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 Koulibaly cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Napoli ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ee9 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 Kalidou Koulibaly ho\u1eb7c Dries Mertens th\u00ec h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i l\u00e0m n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Ancelotti.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/trung-ve-nay-khien-chelsea-phai-chi-65-trieu-bang-o-he-2018-172-184925.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Koulibaly</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal thay Gary Cahill, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Mertens \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm thay v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Morata.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Napoli ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNapoli c\u0169ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Jorginho cho Man City, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Man xanh d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3913","checkdouble":"190096"},{"date":"15:42 01/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Martial n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi MU?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/14/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bayern Munich mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Old Trafford nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-tien-dao-martial-tuyen-bo-chia-tay-mu-172-188440.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anthony Martial tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi MU</span>, theo \u0111\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern Munich mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bayern Munich mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial s\u1ebd d\u1ee9t \u00e1o chia tay MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Martial c\u00f2n x\u1ebfp sau Rashford trong vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Sanchez.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn Martial b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Ph\u00e1p d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ee9t \u00e1o ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i, \u1edf Anh Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Tottenham ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ef1u sao Monaco. B\u00ean ngo\u00e0i bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, Juventus, Bayern v\u00e0 PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Martial v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u euro</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayern Munich mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Old Trafford nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial chiem tron mat bao trong lan dau ra mat\" title=\"Martial chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ra m\u1eaft\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-156,-tin-nong-chuyen-nhuong-he-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Martial\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDaily Star kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern \u0111\u00e3 \u00e2m th\u1ea7m g\u1eb7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Martial, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, Bayern ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang nh\u1eafm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995. Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3912","checkdouble":"190097"},{"date":"10:57 01/07","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Th\u00e1i Lan: B\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 cho tham v\u1ecdng World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/u19-viet-nam-dau-u19-thai-lan-buoc-chay-da-cho-tham-vong-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 10 t\u1edbi v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef3 t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 duy\u00ean n\u1ee3 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018.</h2><h2>K\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u, th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng t\u1ea1o c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i Bahrain khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u \u00c1. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n b\u1edfi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng l\u00ec l\u1ee3m v\u00e0 ngoan c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t xa t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec chung cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U19 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y \u00c1 l\u00e0 U.A.E v\u00e0 Iraq.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan B\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 cho tham v\u1ecdng World Cu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan B\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 cho tham v\u1ecdng World Cu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/28/U19-Viet-Nam-vs-U19-Thai-Lan-Buoc-chay-da-cho-tham-vong-World-Cu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi k\u1ef3 t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Bahrain. V\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean c\u00fa s\u1ed1c ti\u1ebfp theo khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Tr\u1ea7n Th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n s\u1edf h\u1eefu 1 trong 4 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 n\u0103m sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n v\u1edbi th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng s\u1ebd t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh l\u1ecbch s\u1eed m\u00e0 l\u1ee9a Quang H\u1ea3i, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu,&hellip; \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Bahrain n\u0103m 2016. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eebng c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c hay Morocco c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a \u0111\u00e0n anh hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed5i nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a NHM?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan - c\u1ed1 nh\u00e2n h\u1ed9i ng\u1ed9<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup 2019 b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 duy\u00ean n\u1ee3 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 1/7 t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, trong khu v\u1ef1c, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf m\u1ecdi c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9, t\u1eeb \u0110TQG cho t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2015, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ebd b\u00e0ng 0-6 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"u19 thai lan\" title=\"u19 th\u00e1i lan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/30/micki-khong-hieu-noi-mourinho-dang-nghi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U19 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U18 \u0110N\u00c1 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eafng khi b\u1ecb Myanmar v\u00e0 Indonesia \u0111\u00e1 v\u0103ng kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, trong khi U18 Th\u00e1i Lan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 th\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ea5y tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111ang nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau n\u00e0y, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ecf ra e ng\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Th\u00e1i Lan c\u0169ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1eeb 3, 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ea3.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c em khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho d\u00f9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p Th\u00e1i Lan, Indonesia hay Philippines&quot;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd gi\u1eef v\u1eefng s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin, c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018:&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 1/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Th\u00e1i Lan (SV\u0110 Joko Samudro)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 3/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Philippines (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 5/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 L\u00e0o (SV\u0110 Joko Samudro)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 19h00, 7/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Indonesia (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 8/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Singapore (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-khong-ngai-u19-thai-lan-o-ngay-ra-quan-u19-dna-168-189953.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-khong-ngai-u19-thai-lan-o-ngay-ra-quan-u19-dna.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-khong-ngai-u19-thai-lan-o-ngay-ra-quan-u19-dna-168-189953.html\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n U19 \u0110N\u00c1</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-xem-nhe-u19-viet-nam-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-168-189289.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nguoi-thai-xem-nhe-u19-viet-nam-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-xem-nhe-u19-viet-nam-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-168-189289.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i xem nh\u1eb9 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khu v\u1ef1c s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan, Narakorn Noomchansakul \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U19...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-tre-ha-noi-ap-dao-doi-hinh-u19-viet-nam-du-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-168-189877.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/9/doi-tre-ha-noi-ap-dao-doi-hinh-u19-viet-nam-du-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-tre-ha-noi-ap-dao-doi-hinh-u19-viet-nam-du-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-168-189877.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 t\u1ea1i Indonesia v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3911","checkdouble":"190076"},{"date":"10:56 01/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan 15h30 ng\u00e0y 1/7 (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-15h30-ngay-17.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 l\u00fac 15h30 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 1/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 14/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A c\u00f9ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia, \u0110KV\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan, Singapore, Philippines v\u00e0 L\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng khi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhau. Do \u0111\u00f3, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e1 k\u1ef9 cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan 15h30 chi\u1ec1u h\u00f4m nay 17 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan 15h30 chi\u1ec1u h\u00f4m nay 17 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/u19-viet-nam-u19-tl.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan</h2>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 6 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n 10 ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande (Trung Qu\u1ed1c). C\u00f2n h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 4, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ecd x\u00e1t t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U19 Suwon JS Cup 2018 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i U19 Mexico (thua 0-4), U19 Morocco (1-1) v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (1-1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean quen thu\u1ed9c nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n T\u1edbi, B\u00f9i Ho\u00e0ng Vi\u1ec7t Anh, Nguy\u1ec5n Xu\u00e2n Ki\u00ean, L\u00ea V\u0103n Xu\u00e2n, Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n, Tr\u1ea7n C\u00f4ng Minh... <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam, l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ng\u1eafn, ban b\u1eadt nh\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Chi\u1ec1u nay, khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ed3i ch\u1edd U19 Th\u00e1i Lan h\u1edf s\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup 2017, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch. V\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1i t\u00ean U19 Th\u00e1i Lan. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN C\u1ee6A U19&nbsp; VI\u1ec6T NAM:</strong> Y \u00ca Li Ni \u00ca; V\u0103n Xu\u00e2n, V\u0103n T\u1edbi, Vi\u1ec7t Anh, Quang Vinh; H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n, V\u0103n C\u00f4ng, C\u00f4ng Minh, H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng, Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa, V\u0103n Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018:&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 1/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Th\u00e1i Lan (SV\u0110 Joko Samudro)</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 3/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Philippines (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 5/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 L\u00e0o (SV\u0110 Joko Samudro)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 19h00, 7/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Indonesia (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 8/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Singapore (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan 15h30 ng\u00e0y 17 (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan 15h30 ng\u00e0y 17 (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/TRUC-TIEP-U19-Viet-Nam-vs-U19-Thai-Lan-15h30-ngay-17-(U19-Dong-Nam-A-2018)-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Danh s\u00e1ch U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u19-viet-nam-dau-u19-thai-lan-buoc-chay-da-cho-tham-vong-world-cup-168-190076.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/u19-viet-nam-dau-u19-thai-lan-buoc-chay-da-cho-tham-vong-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u19-viet-nam-dau-u19-thai-lan-buoc-chay-da-cho-tham-vong-world-cup-168-190076.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Th\u00e1i Lan: B\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 cho tham v\u1ecdng World Cup</span><br>\r\n\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 10 t\u1edbi v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef3 t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup hai n\u0103m...</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3910","checkdouble":"190078"},{"date":"11:06 01/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018: Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 - B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng BXH - LT\u0110 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t.</h2>T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 6 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3ng B d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u01a1n khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 5 \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo lu\u1eadt, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 v\u00f2ng tr\u00f2n 1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t, ch\u1ecdn ra 2 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t - nh\u00ec m\u1ed7i b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e9o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 chung k\u1ebft. Theo l\u1ecbch, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 2 ng\u00e0y /tr\u1eadn, m\u1edf m\u00e0n l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi U19 Th\u00e1i Lan. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam l\u00e0 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u1ecd x\u00e1t, th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 r\u00e0 so\u00e1t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Indonesia t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 18/10 \u0111\u1ebfn 4/11/2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChia b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng nam \u00c1 2018:<br>\r\nB\u1ea3ng A: Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Th\u00e1i Lan, Indonesia, Singapore, L\u00e0o, Philippines;<br>\r\nB\u1ea3ng B: Malaysia, Timor Leste, Myanmar, Campuchia, Brunei.<br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Lich-thi-dau-U19-Viet-Nam-tai-giai-U19-Dong-Nam-A-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3909","